snippet.title: Magical Girls vs Cat Aliens   Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: Protect the city from the alien cat invasion! Punish the invaders on the name of love and justice. Defeat every enemy and boss to raise the city's public security level and collect crystals to upgrade your magical wands, each with their own characteristics.
